7 132ND LEGISLATURE
8 FIRST SPECIAL SESSION
9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 601, L.D. 1483, “An Act to Validate
10 Certain Referendum Proceedings Conducted by the City of South Portland”
11 Amend the bill in the emergency preamble by inserting after the 3rd indented paragraph
12 the following:
13 'Whereas, at the same city referendum held November 5, 2024, the voters of the city
14 ratified and approved a charter amendment regarding the disposition of certain city-owned
15 property; and'
16 Amend the bill in the emergency preamble by inserting after the 4th indented paragraph
17 the following:
18 'Whereas, the charter amendment was approved by the voters of the city as follows:
19 11,807 in favor and 2,370 against, with 801 blank ballots; and'
20 Amend the bill in the emergency preamble by striking out all of the 8th indented
21 paragraph (page 1, lines 26 to 28 in L.D.)
22 Amend the bill in section 1 in the 4th line (page 2, line 9 in L.D.) by inserting after the
23 following: "questions" the following: 'and the charter amendment question'
24 Amend the bill in section 1 in the last line (page 2, line 13 in L.D.) by inserting after
25 the following: "ordinances." the following: 'The City of South Portland's charter is amended
26 to reflect the approved changes as set forth in the charter amendment question.'
27 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
28 number to read consecutively.
